be frequently cleaned, supported by a chemical plaque treatment. The author 
emphasizes that on no account prevention can be left to the patient. The 
patients always need to be helped. Finally the logopaedic purpose of the 
Castillo-Moralis palatal plate, as well as the functional use of the surgical 
tongue reduction, are discussed.

